text: Catharina Hesterman (17 September 1902 - 17 July 1982) was a Dutch diver. She competed in the women's 3 metre springboard event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1902 births Category:1982 deaths Category:Dutch female divers Category:Olympic divers of the Netherlands Category:Divers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Amsterdam
